{"tid":1538322,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又一班XX不斷吹和風","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:53.000Z","uid":175623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67b89ac00e109a03d8c001d1082de1492f39ca5e","tid":1538322,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"從來救人，成立獨委會同雙普選先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n有人話打落去我地會輸<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個定義輸？你？泛民？<br />\n<br />\n或者咩叫輸？<br />\n<br />\n一萬義士被捉？<br />\n<br />\n緊急法？解放軍？<br />\n<br />\n人人對輸既定義唔同<br />\n<br />\n今次係一場冇大台既運動<br />\n<br />\n相反贏既定義清晰無比<br />\n<br />\n就算退一萬步暫時冇人上街<br />\n<br />\n五年十年二十年 一日未達到五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n我地都同你挽！<br />\n<br />\nps: 講咗不分化不割蓆 我地就係和勇"},{"pid":"97ff619d89bbe1a78b6eb8334c0b442f052ab313","tid":1538322,"uid":39215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KEpGfs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KEpGfs.jpg&h=b05720c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a70da839a356bbddb161f3042132fdde5b216dc","tid":1538322,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"well said"},{"pid":"94a2a40100f6f64e78be261f151aaace10698dde","tid":1538322,"uid":16513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"一、撤回草案<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二、解散警隊</span></span></strong><br />\n三、撤回暴動定性<br />\n四、釋放義士<br />\n五、落實真普選<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"d8ff5e0b86cc09d4f2eab53fed03f324c96c7238","tid":1538322,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"該把撤回法案換成解散警隊，5-1+1=5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個嗌收工 嗌停 就係有錢佬隻狗<img src=\"/ass